strings:
<voice_0x01001CE1><se_high>Princess Medea: I can't get over it!
Flying through the air is so wonderful!
<voice_0x01001CE2><se_high>Princess Medea: You know, I always dreamt of becoming a bird when I was little.
<voice_0x01001CE3><se_high>Princess Medea: This was before you came to the castle, <hero>.

<voice_0x01001CE4><se_high>Princess Medea: All I did was study every day.
I didn't have anyone to play with.
That's probably why I dreamt of having wings...
<voice_0x01001CE5><se_high>Princess Medea: I'd be able to fly away whenever I wanted.
<voice_0x01001CE6><se_high>Princess Medea: Even with the curse, being able to turn into a bird and fly through the sky is like a dream come true.
<voice_0x01001CE7><se_high>Princess Medea: Do you think we might turn into a fish next?

<voice_0x01001CE8><se_high>Princess Medea: I hope not!
I hate the ocean.

<voice_0x01001CE9><se_high>Princess Medea: Why?
Because I'd sink like a stone.
I can't swim!
